<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Yes, that is Matt Bomer on the cover. The author confirms it here:<br/><br/><a target='_blank' rel='noopener nofollow' href='http://www.alexsanchez.com/whatsnew.htm'>http://www.alexsanchez.com/whatsnew.htm</a><a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Yes, that is Matt Bomer on the cover. The author confirms it here:<br /><br /><a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="http://www.alexsanchez.com/whatsnew.htm">http://www.alexsanchez.com/whatsnew.htm</a><a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
